Package org.apache.click.examples.interceptor

Class ProfilingInterceptor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.click.examples.interceptor.ProfilingInterceptor
All Implemented Interfaces:
PageInterceptor
public class ProfilingInterceptor extends Object implements PageInterceptor
Provides a basic page profiling PageInterceptor example.

This interceptor must be configured with "request" scope as it not thread safe.
